text: The Sultanpuri Koli (also spelled as Sultanpure Koli) is a clan (Gotra, Kutumb) of the Koli caste mostly found in the Indian state of Himachal Pradesh and Union Territory of Jammu and Kashmir and nearby. Sultanpuri Kolis drived their name from the Sultanpur village in Himachal Pradesh. == References == Category:Koli clans
title: Sultanpuri Koli
